name: LungeChallenge
0:
”Alexa, open lunge challenge!”
”Alexa, ask lunge challenge to give my daily workout”
”Alexa, tell lunge challenge I have finished my workout.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lunge challenge
des:
Lunges are a good exercise for strengthening, sculpting and building several muscles/muscle groups, including the quadriceps (or thighs), the gluteus maximus (or buttocks) as well as the hamstrings. The lunge is a basic movement that is fairly simple to do for beginner athletes.
With this skill you will learn how to do 200 lunges in a row. Just ask for your daily workout and don't forget to confirm you did it properly. 

Please write a review if you have any suggestion for the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
